- `CypherClawArt.status_display()` accepts an optional `ollama` argument and renders per-socket health, model names, and latency (or unreachable state).
- `format_half_hour_heartbeat()` now adds an `"ollama"` key to the payload and includes an Ollama summary line in text output.
- Both `/status` and heartbeat paths catch `ollama_health()` exceptions and continue without crashing.
- New integration tests for `/status`/heartbeat/exception behavior are present.

## Completeness
All acceptance points from `specs/t-010@20260408t223256zb-spec.md` are covered by implementation and tests, including graceful degradation paths, model/name rendering, and heartbeat payload key presence. Full-suite test execution was run and passed.

