Changes follow existing daemon conventions for command handling and payload shaping and keep heartbeat event recording through `observatory.record("half_hour_heartbeat_sent", payload)`. The added `ollama` section in `status_display()` remains additive and non-breaking for call sites that omit the new parameter.

## Security
No secrets are introduced. Ollama probes and heartbeat data remain local and read-only; existing environment variable handling and Telegram behavior do not appear to increase attack surface in these touched paths.

